#
# The following sections describe libraries that yauiclient-x11 and
# yauiclient-wayland BUNDLE at install time under /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/.
# Each is built from upstream source by build-libmpv-linux-next.sh and
# packaged into the libmpv runtime tarball that ships with these flavours.
#
# yauiclient-wayland-system does NOT bundle these; it uses the system
# libmpv2 package and the system FFmpeg/libav* packages, whose copyright
# information lives in their own /usr/share/doc/<pkg>/copyright files.
#

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libmpv.so*
Copyright: 2000-2026 mpv developers and contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled libmpv 0.41.0 from https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv
 Built with --disable-gpl flags throughout the toolchain so the resulting
 library is pure LGPL-2.1+ with no GPL-only components. Ships only in
 yauiclient-x11 and yauiclient-wayland.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavcodec.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavformat.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavutil.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavfilter.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libswresample.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libswscale.so*
Copyright: 2000-2026 FFmpeg developers and contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled FFmpeg 8.1 from https://ffmpeg.org/
 Configured with --disable-gpl, --disable-nonfree, so this build excludes
 every GPL-only component (no libpostproc, no x264, no x265, etc.) and
 ships as pure LGPL-2.1+. Ships only in yauiclient-x11 and yauiclient-wayland.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libplacebo.so*
Copyright: 2017-2026 Niklas Haas and libplacebo contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled libplacebo 7.360.x from https://code.videolan.org/videolan/libplacebo
 Built with --disable-vulkan to avoid a Vulkan SDK runtime dependency.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libdav1d.so*
Copyright: 2018-2026 VideoLAN, VideoLabs and dav1d contributors
License: BSD-2-Clause
Comment:
 Bundled libdav1d (AV1 decoder) from https://code.videolan.org/videolan/dav1d

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libluajit-5.1.so*
Copyright: 2005-2026 Mike Pall and LuaJIT contributors
License: MIT
Comment:
 Bundled LuaJIT from https://luajit.org/
 LuaJIT itself is MIT; the embedded Lua interpreter is also MIT.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libjpeg.so.62*
Copyright: 1994-1998, Thomas G. Lane
           2010-2026, D. R. Commander and libjpeg-turbo contributors
License: IJG-and-BSD-3-Clause-and-Zlib
Comment:
 Bundled libjpeg-turbo from https://libjpeg-turbo.org/
 libjpeg-turbo carries the original IJG license, plus BSD-3-Clause for
 the SIMD acceleration code, plus Zlib for the libjpeg-turbo additions.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libdisplay-info.so*
Copyright: 2021-2026 Simon Ser, emersion and libdisplay-info contributors
License: MIT
Comment:
 Bundled libdisplay-info 0.2.x from https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/emersion/libdisplay-info

